column5: Private bath; 4 bedrooms (1 for me, 1 for you, 2 unrented) in 2,500 sqft new upscale house w/ stone island + bar stools, granite counters, breakfast nook, covered patio w/ furniture, large yard, wood/tile/carpet, lots of natural light, located in safe and quiet cul-de-sac.  Various restaurants, shopping, and movie theater nearby.  The house is really quiet. I don't watch TV or play loud music.
column8: Private Bath / Quiet / Clean / New Upscale House
